snippet.title: Dumb Ways to Survive | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Collect, harvest and hunt your way through the wilderness as a bumbling bean trying to stay alive. Will you die a dummy or use your smarts to survive?

Play Dumb Ways to Survive on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81664644

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 260 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
